						"Big Snakeys
					]a
					" in the way. The vertical shaft just before the second Big Snakey has a small section where Rush Jet can be summoned. This lets Mega Man constantly use Rush Jet as a platform when climbing up the thin vertical shaft, saving time over climbing up normally.
					$LF
