					[a href=https://magmmlcontest.miraheze.org/wiki/Shrink rel=noopener external nofollow 
						"Shrink
					]a
					" gives Mega Man the i-frames needed to use Rush Jet zipping across the ceiling of spikes without dying. Magnet Beam provides more vertical and horizontal zipping through the rest of the underwater section as it creates usable platforms off screen. Rush Jet is used to zip past the boss doors with Ice Slasher equipped to get early hits on Mega Water S. The boss is also manipulated to avoid the shield barrier attack since that requires a few extra hits to break.
					$LF
