					"Hyper Storm H
				]dt
				[dd 
					" Magnet Beam is used to zip up past the screen. The second screen isn't immediately skipped as the second ladder provides a better horizontal zipping spot for the room above. After the section with the 
					[a href=https://magmmlcontest.miraheze.org/wiki/Hammer_Joe rel=noopener external nofollow 
						"Hammer Joes
					]a
					", Mega Man uses the Magnet Beam to zip up and then to the right to enter an out of bounds area of the map. To the right of this area is a place to get back in bounds with the spike pit that Mega Man needs to fall down.
					$LF
